sentences: Michael George Browning (born May 26, 1964) is an American heavy metal drummer and vocalist.
Browning started to play drums at 13 years old.
He played in the band from 1984 to 1986 and made one official recording with them, Abominations of Desolation; it was not released until 1991, years after Browning left the band.
